                        <head><hi rend="italic">Messrs. <persName type="from">Conger, Goodnow, and
                                    Seaman</persName> to Mr. <persName type="to">Hay</persName>.</hi></head>
                        <opener><seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg></opener>
                        <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="italic">Shanghai</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1903-10-08"><hi rend="italic">October 8,
                                1903</hi></date>.</dateline></opener>
                        <p>(Messrs. Conger, Goodnow, and Seaman report that the treaty with China
                            has been signed.)</p>
